name: Transferred to 1.14.19.9
classes: Acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen;
With reduced flavin or flavoprotein as one donor, and incorporation of one atom of oxygen into the other donor
comment: Transferred entry: tryptophan 7-halogenase. As oxygen is completely reduced to H2O and is not incorporated into the donor chloride, the enzyme has been transferred to EC 1.14.19.9, tryptophan 7-halogenase
